metadata.name: Pinterstellar
metadata.description:
01 — Pinterstellar

/ pinterest + interstellar /

Happily losing the sense of time when looking for inspiration online; the continuous sense of validation and satisfaction provided by an algorithm working perfectly.

I was scrolling through and lost sense of time. It seemed like a day, a week or a decade had passed when I finally hop off.

[introspectabilia.illo.tv](https://introspectabilia.illo.tv)
